data.description: Nestled in a quiet cul-de-sac of the highly coveted Windermere neighborhood, this stunning MASTER-ON-MAIN home offers an exceptional living experience with loads of custom upgrades throughout the home. As you step inside, the two-story entryway makes a striking impression with a grand staircase, dramatic ceilings and gleaming hardwood flooring. The home features an open floor plan, leading into a double-sided fireside family room enhanced by a wall of windows showcasing the panoramic views of your private backyard.  Seamlessly connecting to the breathtaking kitchen and keeping room. Adorned with sleek and refined features, the kitchen boasts stunning custom white cabinetry, beautiful countertops, high-end Viking appliances, large, customized walk-in pantry and a separate butler’s pantry. Just off the kitchen your banquet-size dining room is ideal for hosting and entertaining guests.  The main level includes the luxurious owner’s suite with a newly updated spa-like bathroom, dual vanities, and custom closet. As you head upstairs following the rich hardwood flooring you will find 2 oversized bedrooms that share a jack and jill bath, an additional bedroom with an ensuite bath, a generous in size bonus/media room and tons of closet storage. Venture down to the recently finished custom basement, to an extension of your living space and a haven for recreation and relaxation. This space has been finished with exceptional finishes that include high-end lighting, rich hardwood flooring and high ceilings. Complete with a well-appointed recreation room, a living area, a large room perfect for your addition of a wet bar or dining space, a custom private gym with beautiful metal doors, oversized bedroom and full bathroom.  Step outside to your private backyard and listen to the sounds of nature and the creek while enjoying a fire in the custom stone firepit area. Don't miss the oversized garage perfect for a golf cart. Be sure to visit all of the wonderful amenities the neighborhood has to offer such as 2 pools, playground, workout facility, 10 lighted tennis courts, pickleball and basketball courts. Closet to highly rated Forsyth County schools!
